<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your Business Profile is Live!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: #111827;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .highlight {
      color: #3b82f6;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #3b82f6;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Pulse</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome to Pulse, {{businessName}}!</h2>
      <p>Your business profile has been successfully published and is now live on the platform.</p>
      
      <h3>Share Your Storefront</h3>
      <p>Your unique business link is ready. Share it on Instagram, WhatsApp, or anywhere your customers hang out!</p>
      
      <div style="background: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 16px; word-break: break-all;">
        <a href="{{storefront_url}}" style="color: #3b82f6; text-decoration: none;">{{storefront_url}}</a>
      </div>

      <h3>What's next?</h3>
      <p>A profile is just the beginning. To truly stand out and capture your customers' attention, <span class="highlight">you need to list your offers</span>.</p>
      
      <p>Businesses with active listings receive <strong>10x more engagement</strong>. Showcase your top products or services right now to start driving discovery and sales!</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{action_url}}" class="button">Create Your First Listing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>We're excited to have you on board!</p>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Pulse. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
